reviewText: Anjelah Johnson has become our household favorite.  She has the ability to be clean and funny, which is certainly a talent in this day and age.  Her different accents are awesome and funny.  We watch her over and over and can not wait until she appears in this area live. Super Awesome followup to her last Dvd!
Title: Anjelah Johnson: The Homecoming Show

reviewText: OK, I bought this because I'm such a huge fan of hers! It was great, loved her skits and stories, and the WAY she tells it! She's VERY FUNNY and loaded with raw talent!  [There's only ONE better than this -- it's her own "That's How We Do It!" dvd! SHE KILLS IT!!!]The seller sent it to me right on time, the disk was loose but not damaged, it played perfectly! Try it, you'll like it! :)
Title: Anjelah Johnson: The Homecoming Show

reviewText: I love this girl. Saw her first special and loved it. I will probably buy any special she releases. Her humor is an acquired taste. One of my friends said she was just OK. I say she is great.
Title: Anjelah Johnson: The Homecoming Show

reviewText: Not up to her first DVD but worth watching
Title: Anjelah Johnson: The Homecoming Show

reviewText: I love Anjelah Johnson, only comedian I love to watch all day. Loved her since she was on Madtv. She really needs her own show aka Bon Qui Qui.
Title: Anjelah Johnson: The Homecoming Show
